Emoji Charts
 

Full Emoji Data

This chart provides a list of the Unicode emoji characters, with images from different vendors, version and source information, default style, and annotations. The ordering of the emoji and the annotations are based on Unicode CLDR data. This list does include the 320 modifier sequences, and the 23 ZWJ sequences.

For information about the images used in these charts, see Emoji Images and Rights. For details about the format and fields, see Emoji Chart Index and UTR #51 Unicode Emoji. See also Submitting Emoji Character Proposals.
